members.name: HTMLSlotElement.name
members.description: DOMString: Can be used to get and set the slot's name.

members.name: HTMLSlotElement.assignedNodes()
members.description: Returns the sequence of elements assigned to this slot, or alternatively the slot's fallback content.

parameters.name: options Optional
parameters.description: An object that sets options for the nodes to be returned. The available options are: flatten: A Boolean indicating whether to return the elements assigned to the slot (if this value is false) or the slot's fallback content (if this value is true). The default is false.
